fields.name: EnableNRRForInboundDecodedMessages
fields.description: The value indicating whether to enable NRR for inbound decoded messages.

fields.name: EnableNRRForInboundEncodedMessages
fields.description: The value indicating whether to enable NRR for inbound encoded messages.

fields.name: EnableNRRForInboundMDN
fields.description: The value indicating whether to enable NRR for inbound MDN.

fields.name: EnableNRRForOutboundDecodedMessages
fields.description: The value indicating whether to enable NRR for outbound decoded messages.

fields.name: EnableNRRForOutboundEncodedMessages
fields.description: The value indicating whether to enable NRR for outbound encoded messages.

fields.name: EnableNRRForOutboundMDN
fields.description: The value indicating whether to enable NRR for outbound MDN.

fields.name: EncryptionCertificateName
fields.description: The name of the encryption certificate.

fields.name: OverrideGroupSigningCertificate
fields.description: The value indicating whether to send or request a MDN.

fields.name: Sha2AlgorithmFormat
fields.description: The Sha2 algorithm format. Valid values are Sha2, ShaHashSize, ShaHyphenHashSize, Sha2UnderscoreHashSize.

fields.name: SigningCertificateName
fields.description: The name of the signing certificate.
